00:12:33.322 --> 00:12:35.613
[croassements]

327
00:12:36.947 --> 00:12:38.947
[grondement du tonnerre]

328
00:12:43.947 --> 00:12:45.988
[bourdonnement de mouches]

329
00:12:53.655 --> 00:12:54.655
